VCynthia Breazeal: So Kismet interacted with people
p49
aVlike kind of a non-verbal child or pre-verbal child,
p50
aVwhich I assume was fitting because it was really the first of its kind.
p51
aVIt didn't speak language, but it didn't matter.
p52
aVThis little robot was somehow able
p53
aVto tap into something deeply social within us \u2014
p54
aVand with that, the promise of an entirely new way
p55
aVwe could interact with robots.
