aa(lp57
VSo over the past several years
p58
aVI've been continuing to explore this interpersonal dimension of robots,
p59
aVnow at the media lab
p60
aVwith my own team of incredibly talented students.
p61
aVAnd one of my favorite robots is Leonardo.
p62
aVWe developed Leonardo in collaboration with Stan Winston Studio.
p63
aVAnd so I want to show you a special moment for me of Leo.
p64
aVThis is Matt Berlin interacting with Leo,
p65
aVintroducing Leo to a new object.
p66
aVAnd because it's new, Leo doesn't really know what to make of it.
p67
aVBut sort of like us, he can actually learn about it
p68
aVfrom watching Matt's reaction.
